<li>2023 Wild Card Series
<ul><li>Game 2 Marlins/Phillies: 1.8 (3.2 million viewers)</li>
<li>Game 1 Marlins/Phillies: 1.7 (3.0 million viewers)</li>
<li>Game 2 Rangers/Rays (ABC): 1.3 (2.2 million viewers)</li>
<li>Game 1 Rangers/Rays (ABC): 1.3 (2.2 million viewers)</li>
<li>Game 2 Blue Jays/Twins: 1.1 (2.0 million viewers)</li>
<li>Game 2 Diamondbacks/Brewers (ESPN2): 1.1 (1.9 million viewers)</li>
<li>Game 1 Diamondbacks/Brewers (ESPN2): 1.1 (1.9 million viewers)</li>
<li>Game 1 Blue Jays/Twins: 1.0 (1.7 million viewers)</li></ul></li></ul>
